400.title: Bad Request
400.details: The request cannot be fulfilled due to bad syntax.

401.title: Unauthorized
401.details: Authentication is required and has failed or has not yet been provided.

402.title: Payment Required
402.details: Payment is required and has failed or has not yet been provided.

403.title: Forbidden
403.details: The request was a valid request, but the server is refusing to respond to it.

404.title: Not Found
404.details: The requested resource could not be found but may be available again in the future.

405.title: Method Not Allowed
405.details: A request was made of a resource using a request method not supported by that resource.

406.title: Not Acceptable
406.details: The requested resource is only capable of generating content not acceptable.

407.title: Proxy Authentication Required
407.details: Proxy authentication is required and has failed or has not yet been provided.

408.title: Request Timeout
408.details: The server did not receive a complete request details in time.

409.title: Conflict
409.details: The request could not be processed because of conflict in the request.

410.title: Gone
410.details: The requested resource is no longer available and will not be available again.

411.title: Length Required
411.details: The request did not specify the length of its content, which is required by the resource.

412.title: Precondition Failed
412.details: The server does not meet one of the preconditions that the requester put on the request.

413.title: Payload Too Large
413.details: The server cannot process the request because the request payload is too large.

414.title: URI Too Long
414.details: The request-target is longer than the server is willing to interpret.

415.title: Unsupported Media Type
415.details: The request entity has a media type which the server or resource does not support.

417.title: Expectation Failed
417.details: The expectation given could not be met by at least one of the inbound servers.

418.title: I'm a teapot
418.details: The server refuses the attempt to brew coffee with a teapot.

421.title: Misdirected Request
421.details: The request was directed at a server that is not able to produce a response.

422.title: Unprocessable Entity
422.details: The request was well-formed but was unable to be followed due to semantic errors.

423.title: Locked
423.details: The resource that is being accessed is locked.

424.title: Failed Dependency
424.details: The request failed due to failure of a previous request.

425.title: Too Early
425.details: The server is unwilling to risk processing a request that might be replayed.

426.title: Upgrade Required
426.details: The server cannot process the request using the current protocol.

428.title: Precondition Required
428.details: The origin server requires the request to be conditional.

429.title: Too Many Requests
429.details: The user has sent too many requests in a given amount of time.

431.title: Request Header Fields Too Large
431.details: The server is unwilling to process the request because its header fields are too large.

451.title: Unavailable For Legal Reasons
451.details: The server is unwilling to process the request due to legal reasons.

500.title: Internal Server Error
500.details: An error has occurred and this resource cannot be displayed.

501.title: Not Implemented
501.details: The server either does not recognize the request method, or it lacks the ability to fulfil the request.

502.title: Bad Gateway
502.details: The server was acting as a gateway or proxy and received an invalid response from the upstream server.

503.title: Service Unavailable
503.details: The server is currently unavailable. It may be overloaded or down for maintenance.

504.title: Gateway Timeout
504.details: The server was acting as a gateway or proxy and did not receive a timely response from the upstream server.

505.title: HTTP Version Not Supported
505.details: The server does not support the HTTP protocol version used in the request.

506.title: Variant Also Negotiates
506.details: The server has an internal configuration error relating to content negotiation.

507.title: Insufficient Storage
507.details: The server has an internal configuration error relating to free memory.

508.title: Loop Detected
508.details: The server detected an infinite loop while processing the request.

510.title: Not Extended
510.details: Further extensions to the request are required for the server to fulfill it.

511.title: Network Authentication Required
511.details: The client needs to authenticate to gain network access.
